## Baishilefye na inkwela shakusolelako amabwe ne impikiso, elyo na imipini ilya batila long baton
## Ba Mubailo bapulikilwa umulemba mukutwi
## Kuti bati batiile baumfwkofye ba mpemba-mfyone balatikuka na tikuuu nge minshinga ne mifwi na mafumo yalalakatafye nga amabwe ya mfula apo babelele
 ## Ala mukwai baishiba ne lyashi abati kaboobwa, leelo fyayaluka imono
## Umusambo kolwe anasha uyo lyonse angalapo leelo wakooboka, natwime tulupite yemwe twaingililwa
## Cilya ba Mubailo basheta ulushishi ifita nabankole bonse babombela capamo bafulamuna na cimotoka pakuti bekabwela nakabili
## Ilyo ba Mubailo baileshina kuli babwana kapaso wabo, kwati nimbwa shapusuka kuli ngoshe, abasungu balisakameene saana pakumona ifyo icipekeni ca Chachacha ica kulwila ubuntungwa cakaba
## Elyo napamulandu wakuti abasungu balemona ukuti bankosa-mukanwa pafya buntungwa bafulile ku bu Bemba ukubikapofye ne ncende sha ku Bulozi naku Butonga, kuli Balubale naku Ngoni kanshi bafwile ukutekanya pakucimfya ubu bulwi
## Mu caalo Chishinga pali ilya inshita mwalipo umukandi umo ifi untutwingatilafye ati afyelwe icikalasama nangu icikata-insoka, umuntu uwakakaata, ushaletina fiswango bulwani bonse
## Uyu mulumendo, ishina ati Chikondo-cimo, Lesa-mukulu amubumbile fimbi ifyo abantu bambi abalengele, ali icilema
## Akwete icikondo cimo ku Lusaka lumo, lumbi ulukasa lwalifye bwino, lelo umubili wakwe walifye uwa kalabana, aya ukubengeshima nga mamba ya nsoka
## Lelo nanguline ali nobululema ali uwakalabana mumucitiley akwe, uwakaata, kaafwa uwalecimfya amaafya abantu bampempeele balefilwa elyo kabili uwalubilo nganshi nge cisekesa
## Uyu musambashi panshita imo alipapwishe icaalo ilyo bakapenda-mabuula baali muncende ilya, balelonda impanga nokwikata abaletema ifitemene na abaletapa inama sha mpanga
## Ilyo baleyabuka Uluongo mubwato umo pali aba bakapenda-mabuula imfuti yakwe yaishilepusumuka noku solomokela peshiba, cabipa nokubipa
## Mu Chishinga tamwali nangu umo uwali no bulamba bwakwibila muli uyu mumana pa mulandu wa fiswango fyalimo
## Kuti umo baletaba-taba akalimbusha akati uyu mulimo tapali no umo uwinga ucimfya, kanofye chikondo-cimo 
## Awe mukwai nokumyanaga umucele kashita batuma ne nkombe yaku leta chikondo-cimo kwa Santimu
## Ilyo uyu mukandi bamuletele bamulangile napa ncende apo imfuti yatobeele, ninshi ni mumana walipabuka, walibunda waliposa nafilya
## Li Chikondo-cimo, ukwabula nokuti litale litontonkanyepo, iyasamwina lyaipoola na petenga kuti na pooo nge cibokolo, lyaibila
## Ala mukwai pano caalo palilawa, paaba abantu imisango pabili na patatu, Chikondo-cimo aibila nge nondo pe tenga, panshi ya mumana
## Napo nga ali nicisanguka, ninshi ni mucinama nshi? Nalimo ali na mansangala nge sabi umwakupeemena, 
## teeti twishibe pantu inshita aposele panshi ya menshi ilyo alefwaya imfuti ukwabula ikwibuka ala yakupapa, mwababile
## Aishile tumpukafye limbi-limbi ninshi na ba kapenda-mabuula nabasakamana abati nalimo umuntu wabene nanwena, 
## nangu nabamulya ku fiswango fya mu longo, nokubeeba ati imfuti ali naisanga kanshi ali nokuya abula panuma ya kukola umwela
## Cilya atusha Chikondo-cimo aipolapo nakabili, nacine kuti bati batiile bamona fye uyu aibuka, aisa aletaakanya ne mufti ine, abatambika abuka aikala na pacaani alafuula ne nsuli
## Ilyo aba bakapenda-mabuula baipwishe icilambu balelomba ku buteeko pakwabula icibombele ca kamfulumende ba Chikondo-cimo beena baaswike abati: 
## lyoo mukwai bampele fye konse ako bapekeenye ku luse lwabo, mwebeena-mfumu
## Kucamupamba nangu icansoni saana icilambu cafumishe balya babomfi babuteeko califye macampa yalya yene ba kapenda-mabuula bafwala pancito mu mpanga, eyo bafyankile Chikondo-cimo
## Lelo nanguline ba Chikondo-cimo camoneke ukuti tabacengele icilambu abekala mushi calibakalipe pa kaso ka babomfi babuteeko
## Nabo batiilefye ati cinecine bacenjelela ing’anga
## Chikondo-cimo alesambilila pa Kuyumba
## Nangu ali uwashipa kukushokana nefinjelengwe fya mumumana ne mpanga, ukumutotosha ifikoti ku matako kuli ba kafundisha fyena talefwaya nagufye panoono
## Kanshi aleti nga alufyanya cimo ba kafundisha babuula ubwembya “Chikondo” ena kulompokela napa windo, alufonkols ukulola nakukwabuka Uluongo pambilibili
## Cilya bakafundisha basoweshako abanankwe ukuti bamwikate ala mukwai, alebutuka nge cibanda camuli Ole
## Kusangafye li “Chikondo” nalisotola notwakufwala, nalikakila napa mutwe lili napakati kabakateya wa mupila ilyo umulumendo baleita peshina lya boola at mayouwakalabana ku mingalato uwamwibumba lyaba kalundu bamukwempele umweleka nangu ulukooka ayawa icikako bubi-bubi, uku ninshi abeena-Kuyumba baleimba no lwimbo lwakutumfya abati: 
## Leelo kuleba ukubobana naya amakula
## Leelo kuleba ukubobana 	
## Leelo kukuleba
## Leelo kuleba ukubobana!
## Mayo fye eka ewalefwala insondolo nangu imponti shakuteelamo impila, abashala balekakafye ifikumba kufikondo nakumakufi
## Kanshi ekutila Mayo baletina nokumufikapo nganakwata impila
## Lelo kwaliko no munyamata balelumba abati Kabulubulu Munshitiina-mulinso-lya mfumu, uwatusafu nge cimpombwa kabiliuwashangila,muli ba Kuyumba, ena atile Mayo ni uko kwine bamucoonga na kamunga ke sabi, lelo alelobamo ilyauma,pamwandi talalanyepo, pali ulukose
## Na cine ilyo uyu mulumendo aishile nga akamimbi alekasa bambi ukwisa mukwingisha impila kabulu-bulu aishile mwingilamo na kasembe, amukwempa awa no bunseneme nga chituku anwene ubuuba 
## Ata mukwai nefintu fyapena ilyo kasongelekanya umo ifi pakumona ifyo impaalume yakwe baifwampula, akuwisha ati: Pumuneni ba makaka! 
## Kasongelekanya fyakapitamo na Chikondo-cimo, fyatamfyanya ukulola ku mumana, lelo namumfwa nokuti “Chikondo” nga alola ku mumana ninshi mwebo bwelenikofye
## Bakafundisha mukalamba ba mubanga Mubanga Pulula abeena-Chishinga bonteko insansu, ba pa Kuyumba baali nibanshilingwa kani mwikufi awe fyalimbana no mulumendo umo ifi uwafumine ku kalaale uwaleita ati Tarzan 
## Ala mukwai nifilya batilapalwila insofu can eciculilamo
## Uyu mulumendo Tarzan uko akulile ku kalaale alisambilile amabokoseni, ulubuli lwa basungu ulwa nkonya 
## Kanshi ba mubanga Pulula nanguline baali abamaka ngashi awe mukwai nifilya batila mwine mushi tabifya masha kanshi abeena- Kuyumba balibaleba
## Panuma ya ulu lubuli abena Kuyumba ekuyaobola ba kapokola ku Mwense ukuti bese nokufulula abena kalundu

